{"tid":2442532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★專家指本港疫苗接種未如理想 須調整策略；例如為所有與長者同住的人接種","createTime":"2021-03-11T11:59:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T12:04:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c45b718c473572da56ff1de301152d722ed8d071","tid":2442532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"衞生防護中心轄下科學委員會的專家劉宇隆認為，本港疫苗接種進度未如理想，有必要調整策略，包括擴大接種的群組，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>例如為所有與長者同住或照顧他們的人接種。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心轄下科學委員會專家劉宇隆則認為，本港疫苗接種進度未如理想，有必要調整策略，要有效保護長者免受感染，他建議當局優先為所有與長者同住人士、外傭或照顧者接種。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/local/6049f240335d193f47bb23a2/%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%AA%E5%A6%82%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3-%E9%A0%88%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F6049f240335d193f47bb23a2%2F%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%258B%2597%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25A6%2582%25E7%2590%2586%25E6%2583%25B3-%25E9%25A0%2588%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%2595%25B4%25E7%25AD%2596%25E7%2595%25A5%25E6%2593%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258E%25A5%25E7%25A8%25AE%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%25B5%2584&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=648bcd46\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/local/6049f240335d193f47bb23a2/%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E6%8C%87%E6%9C%AC%E6%B8%AF%E7%96%AB%E8%8B%97%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E9%80%B2%E5%BA%A6%E6%9C%AA%E5%A6%82%E7%90%86%E6%83%B3-%E9%A0%88%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E7%AD%96%E7%95%A5%E6%93%B4%E5%A4%A7%E6%8E%A5%E7%A8%AE%E7%BE%A4%E7%B5%84</a>"},{"pid":"e9ef81a9e10cb745daf91f12c85267e645284adf","tid":2442532,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass